{"title":"战士二题","authors":["向灿辉"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":2,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士二题\t向灿辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的肩膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是什么铸成战士的肩膀？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——燃烧的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严峻的冰霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炽热的战火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛烈的风浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特殊的材料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百炼的精钢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是什么担在战士的肩上？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——火红的旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪亮的刀枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级的重任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的理想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的前途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的希望……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的脚板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的一双铁脚板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吻着祖国的万水千山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一句庄严的誓词，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一个战斗的鼓点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从黑夜走到火红的黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从严冬走到温暖的春天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩出了一条宽广的大道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏平了三座险恶的大山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找不到哪里是起点终点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只看见有一根鲜明红线："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一头系着祖国苦难过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一头系着人类幸福明天！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}